pipeline

| Behavior                   | MVP Detection                       |
| -------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| No face                    | face missing for X seconds          |
| Different person           | face embedding mismatch             |
| Looking away               | head/gaze angle exceeds threshold   |
| Bad posture / leaving seat | upper body/keypoints abnormal       |
| Multiple faces             | more than one face detected         |
| Suspicious pattern         | repeated flags within a time window |

